vl's.<br>-neutral/good alighments(and everything in between)<br>-You like to have fun<br>-you arn't a powergaming fiend.<br><br>I hope many of you join. I am of the 31st season right now.<br><br>I will not be online until friday because my game card ran out =( and i dont get money till friday. So reply to this post and try msging Ezekiell. Who is going to be guild leader.<br><br>Hope to see you in guild =) <br><br>Please post reply's here over msging ezekiell as he isnt going to be on much this week. <p><b> Solafein X'tael <b><b> FV Server <b></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usolafeinxtael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SolafeinXtael</A> at: 5/18/02 3:13:22 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usolafeinxtael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SolafeinXtael</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/17/02 6:24:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=165.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Defenders of Truth - RP guild info</span><hr size=1> So no one is intrested? no one at all?<br><br>heh.  <br><br>Crappy!! <p><b> Solafein X'tael <b></br><b> Scout of Tunare </b></br><b> 31st season </b></br><b> FV Server <b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umadrain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>madrain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Kerran Lord</span><br>  Posts: 343<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/18/02 12:13:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=165.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Defenders of Truth - RP guild info</span><hr size=1> Here's my thoughts, if you don't mind me sharing:<br><br>Try changing your level limit!<br><br>I know that while you may want to keep a centralized force of people that can hunt around each other, going to 25 unguilded is not something alot of people might want to do.  There's lots of other 'good' guilds out there with lower limits that can help them get gear, give advice, and group with them before 25.<br><br>I'd just suggest lowering it a little.  Just starting out and don't want transient players?  Maybe...15?  Even 20 would help to get fresh blood in.<br><br>Aside from that, everything sounds wonderful.  I really hope you get this off the ground, as we need some good guilds that will get out there and battle evil - not just good/neutral guilds that live and let live.  I'm still waiting for some righteous fanatic of Mithaniel Marr to come slice their way through evil!<br><br>After all, it's hard to be a knight of evil when the few paladins you run across are too afraid to /duel you! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usolafeinxtael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SolafeinXtael</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/18/02 3:00:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=165.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Defenders of Truth - RP guild info</span><hr size=1> <br>Thank you for the advice madrain I never thoiugh of it that way.<br>You make a good point, and now that I think about it I can't really remember seeing anyone post-25 with out a guild.<br>I like the sound of lvl 15 minimum. Is there any point in starting a guild at level 31 and expecting to get a good base of players at your level? Or will I have to rely on other people leveling